metadata.name: Dori 1776 #1
metadata.description: The 2nd generation Dori 1776 collection introduces female Dori street samurai and augments the cyberpunk futuristic lore as The House of Dori continues to build out brand partnership, metaverse applications, anime/comics and more. Holders of both the Genesis and the 1776 Collections will have exclusive benefits and utility for life which include Access, Tools, $DORI, Exclusive Alpha and much more. While unannounced, Dori Samurai aims to make the collection(s) deflationary by introducing a 3rd generation which will require decisions on burning tokens alongside the use of native token $DORI.
